h4. Actor:
Administrator.

h4. Description:
Name of use case represents its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [Exchange House|guide:_ShowExchangeHousePlugin] option from top menu bar.
* Click "Report" sub menu from left menu.
* Click "Remittance Transaction" link.
* [Show Landing Page of "Remittance Transaction" Report|guide:ExhShowRemittanceTransactionActionService].
* Enter valid input.
* Click "PDF" icon of the upper right side of the page.
* System will show confirmation message of download.
* Actor clicks "Ok" button.
* Download "Remittance Transaction" Report in PDF Format.

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Download Remittance Transaction" privilege.
* Follow rules of validation:
{table}
 *Field* | *Input Type* | *Data Type* | *Rules* 
 Start Date | Calender | Date | Required
 End Date | Calender | Date | Required
 Amount Higher or Equal | Text Box | Numeric | Required
{table}


h4. Process:
* Download the report as PDF format.
* PDF header should show company name.
* PDF footer should show page no, print date.

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** PDF Report will successfully download to user's computer.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

